<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h3 class="header-about-me">About Me</h3>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="margin-btm-sm">
          <!-- <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmx0a3nqi/image/upload/v1560695906/Photo_on_13-05-2019_at_12.07_PM_2.jpg" width="100%" height="100%" alt="Profile Image" /> -->
          <%= image_tag "profile-image-1.jpg", width: 400, alt: "profile image", class: "profile-img" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#personal-statement"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="personal-statement"
          >
            About me
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#skills"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="skills"
          >
            Skills
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Andela
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Abutech
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Unizik - BSC Computer Engineering
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              CIC - WASSC
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="skills collapse" id="skills">
            <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <p><strong><%= skill.title %></strong></p>
              <div class="progres">
                <div class="progress">
                  <div class="progress-bar bg-info" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                    aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>%" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>

          <div class="personal-statement collapse" id="personal-statement">
            <p>
                I enjoy who I am as a programmer. Programming has helped me develop valuable personal characters.
                Itâ€™s effect on my life transcends the professional arena. I have developed good relationships and
                sustained them by applying, sometimes subconsciously, the same techniques I use to solve a programming
                challenge; techniques like defining the problem and identifying the parameters at play, determining
                concrete specific steps to solve the problem and applying those steps systematically to come up with
                a solution. Such methods do more than produce algorithms, they also produce good personal and
                professional relationships, resulting in a happier, more productive life. 
            </p>
            <p>
              I have had bugs that took me days to solve, and I have had personal issues that took a while to resolve. Both required same technique - patience
              and persistence. I am a programmer because I like who I am when I think like one.
            </p>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


